            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1637671516870-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> ground coriander</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>,<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>and<strong> white long grain rice </strong>to the dish</p><p>Add 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with your<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for 25-30 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1637671536325-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1637671536325-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1637671536325-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1637671536325-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1637671536325-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained sweetcorn </strong>to a serving bowl with <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), the juice of<strong> half</strong> the <strong>lime[s] </strong>and a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>then crumble over your <strong>feta</strong></p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>esquites</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1637671563252-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1637671563252-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1637671563252-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1637671563252-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1637671563252-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything's cooked through, remove the dish from the oven</p><p>Shred the <strong>cooked chicken</strong> apart using two forks and fluff the rice<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>smoky coriander chicken & rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1637671601705-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1637671601705-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1637671601705-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1637671601705-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1637671601705-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, garnish the <strong>smoky coriander chicken & rice </strong>with the <strong>remaining chopped coriander </strong>and the<strong> lime wedges</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>esquites </strong>to the side</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
      "order": 8,
